OL,3,CDeadline to record historic paths to
OL,4,Cbe scrapped under government plans
OL,6,FThe government plans to repeal a cut-
OL,7,Foff date for registering historic
OL,8,Fpaths in a move that walking
OL,9,Fenthusiasts have hailed as a
OL,10,F"fantastic step" for people to enjoy
OL,11,Fnature.
OL,13,FIn an announcement timed to mark the
OL,14,Ftraditional Boxing Day ramble, the
OL,15,FDepartment for Environment Food and
OL,16,FRural Affairs (Defra) said the removal
OL,17,Fof the deadline for registering
OL,18,Fthousands of miles of rights of way
OL,19,Fmeant they would no longer be lost to
OL,20,Fthe public.
