OL,3,CDeadline to record historic paths to
OL,4,Cbe scrapped under government plans
OL,6,FSome of these paths, well used by
OL,7,Fwalkers, cyclists and equestrians,
OL,8,Fdate back hundreds or even thousands
OL,9,Fof years, but are not officially
OL,10,Frecorded or protected.
OL,12,FOnce recorded as rights of way and
OL,13,Fadded to the definitive map, paths are
OL,14,Fprotected under the law for people to
OL,15,Fuse.
