OL,3,CDeadline to record historic paths to
OL,4,Cbe scrapped under government plans
OL,6,FThe last government said it would
OL,7,Frepeal a 2026 deadline for registering
OL,8,Fmore than 40,000 miles of unregistered
OL,9,Fpaths amid what campaigners described
OL,10,Fas a "race against time" to get them
OL,11,Fon the official map.
OL,13,FBut it later reversed that decision
OL,14,Fand instead extended the cut-off date
OL,15,Fto 2031 for recording historic rights
OL,16,Fof way for people to ensure access
OL,17,Falong them - a deadline that the new
OL,18,Fgovernment has now said it would
OL,19,Frepeal when parliamentary time allowed.
