OL,6,F"These well-trodden routes, many of
OL,7,Fwhich have been in place for hundreds
OL,8,Fof years, are a part of our shared
OL,9,Fheritage and it is critical that we
OL,10,Fbring forward these measures to
OL,11,Fprotect their long-term future."
OL,13,FRoss Maloney, chief executive of The
OL,14,FRamblers, said: "The government's
OL,15,Fdecision to end the threat to
OL,16,Fthousands of miles of historic rights
OL,17,Fof way in England is a fantastic step
OL,18,Fforward in making sure everyone can
OL,19,Fenjoy the benefits of walking in
OL,20,Fnature.
