OL,6,F"Not only are these paths an integral
OL,7,Fpart of our shared heritage, but they
OL,8,Fwill also have a critical role to play
OL,9,Fin the future by helping people live
OL,10,Fhealthier, happier lives."
OL,12,FBut the Country Land and Business
OL,13,FAssociation's deputy president Gavin
OL,14,FLane described it as a backward step
OL,15,Fand the "latest attack" on the
OL,16,Fcountryside and farmers.
