OL,3,CDeadline to record historic paths to
OL,4,Cbe scrapped under government plans
OL,6,F"Campaigners have had decades to
OL,7,Frecord rights of way, and the decision
OL,8,Fto scrap the 2031 cut-off date has
OL,9,Fbeen made without engaging with those
OL,10,Fwho will be affected, inflicting
OL,11,Fsignificant uncertainty on farmers and
OL,12,Fland managers," he said.
OL,14,F"The vast majority of landowners are
OL,15,Fkeen to promote responsible access,
OL,16,Fand work in collaboration with Defra
OL,17,Fand campaigning groups to ensure
OL,18,Fpeople can continue to experience the
OL,19,Fbenefits of the countryside in decades
OL,20,Fto come."
